comment.author: 82797434@N02
comment._content: Not sure what this is but it is not a BF-110 cockpit, may be a ME-108 cockpit.  Note the single two bladed prop, side by side controls and single set of engine instruments.  The Me-110 would have had two engines one on either side of the cockpit with three bladed props, single pilot controls and two sets of engine instruments.
